quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  39,22,"E ko on mo Allah ya√±√±ani …ìendre mun nden, fii lislaamu, hara himo e ndaygu immorde ka Joomi makko... Bone woodanii …ìen yooru…ìe …ìer…óe mun, e jantagol Allah. ∆Åen wonii e majjere …ìanngunde"
  39,23,"Allah jippinii ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e yewtere, Deftere nanndunde [√±aawooje], …óimmitunde. Nde guri …ìen huloo…ìe Joomi mun ri…ìirta (nanugol nde), refti guri e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe dee∆¥ira jantoore Allah nden. Ko …óum woni peewal Allah ngal O fewnirta on Mo muuyani. Kala non mo Allah majjini, haray fewnoowo mo alaa"
  39,24,"E ko on reentarii…óo yeeso mun ngon, e lepte bon…óe …óen √ëalnde Darngal... Too√±u…ìe …ìen wi'anee ontuma: \"Mee…óee kon ko wonuno…óon faggitanaade"
  39,25,"Adinoo…ìe …ìen fenniino, lepte …óen ardirani …ìe, ka …ìe so'aa-anndude"
  39,26,"Allah mee…óiniri …ìe koyeera, ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet non, ko lepte laakara …óen non, …ìuri mawnude, si tawno hi…ìe anndunoo"
  39,27,"Gom…óii Men piyanii yim…ìe …ìen, e ndee Alqur'aanaare, kala misal, belajo'o, …ìe waajitora"
  39,28,"Alqur'aanaare (janngeteende) e haala Aarabu, nde aldaa e oo√±aare, fii no …ìe gom…óira"
  39,29,"Allah wa…óii misal, gorko mo lurru…ìe hawti …óum, hi…ìe poo…óondira mo, e gorko laa…ìan…óo gorko [goo]: Hara …ìen …ói…óo fotay e misal? Yettoore woodanii Allah! Kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe anndaa"
  39,30,"Pellet, ko a maayoowo, kam…ìe kadi ko …ìe maayoo…ìe"
  39,31,"refti onon, √ëalnde Darngal, ko ka Joomi mon, yeddondiroyton"
